cy.get('.header__nav > :nth-child(1) > .header__lineOne').should('contain.text', 'Welcoem');

//page object olusturma
const homePage = new _HomePage.default(); //loginPage object olusturma

homePage.getSigninLink().click(); //username gir
loginPage.getUserNameBox().type(this.data.username); //username girildigini dogrula
loginPage.getUserNameBox().should('have.attr', 'value', this.data.username); //password gir
loginPage.getPasswordBox().type(this.data.password); //password girildigini dogrula

loginPage.getLoginButton().click(); //giris yapildigini onayla
loginPage.getWelcomeText().should('contain.text', 'Welcome'); //giris yapildigini assert etme
loginPage.getNavbarHeader().should('contain.text', 'Welcome').and('contain.text', 'React').and('contain.text', 'Logout').and('contain.text', this.data.username);
